      "content": "hey, my family is planning a big move soon and i'm kinda overwhelmed lol. can u help me look for some school districts? we really need places that are known for being super safe, high-achieving, and just have a really strong community feel where kids can grow up in a stable environment. i'm looking at a few different states like texas or north carolina so any good areas that fit that vibe would be great.",
