      "content": "thanks for those! plano and cary seem like good starts. i was also looking at some more diverse areas in those states, like some parts of austin or maybe raleigh itself, but i'm a little worried about how those might compare in terms of safety and academic rigor compared to the ones u mentioned. do u think it's better to stick to those more established, suburban areas to make sure the kids have a really stable, high-performing environment?",
